  "text": "According to [CITATION_1] , BACILLARIOPHYTA consists of three classes: centric diatoms with radial and bipolar symmetry of frustules (class Coscinodiscophyceae Round & Crawford) and two classes of pennate diatoms differing in presence (Bacillariophyceae Haeckel) or absence of a raphe (Fragilariophyceae Round).",
